   Tours
   Want to visit Metz?
   With our smartphone apps… let us guide you around the city and discover
   its historic heritage!
   All essentials
     *
   METZ TOUR

METZ TOUR
       With the application Metz Tour (Mobitour), discover the essentials
       of Metz and surroundings like Nancy, Luxembourg, Trier, Saarbrücken
       (museums, monuments, accommodation, restaurants, shopping, leisure,
       events, tours...).
       Further information
     *
   MONUMENT TRACKER®

MONUMENT TRACKER®
       With the application Metz Monument Tracker®, you are notified of
       the squares, monuments, statues, fountains, places and other
       landmarks close to you with their geolocation, history, a
       description, some anecdotes…
       Further information

