Essentials

   Essentials
   Must-see sights!Centre Pompidou-Metz, Saint-Etienne cathedral, marina,
   mirabelle plum festival, Christmas markets… everything you need for a
   great stay in Metz.

   Essentials
     * SAINT ETIENNE'S CATHEDRAL

SAINT ETIENNE'S CATHEDRAL
       Offers 6500 m2 of stained glass windows from the 13th to the 20th
       century (Valentin Bousch, Marc Chagall, Jacques (...)
       THE CENTRE POMPIDOU-METZ

THE CENTRE POMPIDOU-METZ
       A modern and contemporary art space, covered by a striking roof
       reminiscent of a Chinese hat.
       THE COUR D'OR MUSEUM

THE COUR D'OR MUSEUM
       Gallo-Roman collections, ancient thermal baths, medieval and
       Renaissance architecture, Fine Arts Museum.

